<D>__{fuck miss ratched!}
<A>__{mcmurphy crosses out and up the stairs. the acutes look at each other. a beat, then:}
<C>__{mcmurphy }
<D>__{wow! look at this!}
<A>__{the acutes don't move.}
<C>__{mcmurphy }
<D>__{hey, you guys, come on up here and take a gander at this!}
